import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import ApiService from '../../services/ApiService'; import { useError } from '../common/ErrorDisplay'; const AdminPaymentDetailPage = () => { const { id } = useParams(); const [payment, setPayment] = useState(null); const { ErrorDisplay, showError } = useError(); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { fetchPayment(); }, [id]); const fetchPayment = async () => { try { const response = await ApiService.getAPaymentById(id); if (response.statusCode === 200) { setPayment(response.data); } } catch (error) { showError(error.response?.data?.message || error.message); } }; if (payment) { return (

Payment Details #{payment.id}

Payment Date: {new Date(payment.paymentDate).toLocaleString()}
Status: {payment.paymentStatus}
Amount: ${payment.amount.toFixed(2)}
Payment Gateway: {payment.paymentGateway}
Transaction ID: {payment.transactionId}
Successful: {payment.success ? 'Yes' : 'No'}

Order Information

Order ID: #{payment.order.id}
Order Date: {new Date(payment.order.orderDate).toLocaleString()}
Total Amount: ${payment.order.totalAmount.toFixed(2)}
Order Status: {payment.order.orderStatus.replace('_', ' ')}

Customer Information

Name: {payment.user.name}
Email: {payment.user.email}
Phone: {payment.user.phoneNumber}
Address: {payment.user.address}

Order Items

{payment.order.orderItems.map(item => ( ))}
Item Price Quantity Subtotal
{item.menu.name}
{item.menu.description}
 ${item.pricePerUnit.toFixed(2)} {item.quantity} ${item.subtotal.toFixed(2)}
); } } export default AdminPaymentDetailPage;
